    <div class="container">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
            <h2>Join the Growing Movement</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #666; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
                We're not building an empire—we're planting a forest where everyone can thrive. 
                A Curious Tractor exists to transfer power, not hold it. To amplify voices, not speak for others.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div style="background: var(--act-seedling); color: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 3em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--act-seedling);">◆</div>
                <h3 style="color: white;">Plant a Seed</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">Have a community-led initiative that needs the right conditions to grow? Let's cultivate it together.</p>
                <a href="mailto:hello@act.place" class="btn" style="background: white; color: var(--act-seedling);">Share Your Seed</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: var(--act-sunrise); color: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 3em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: white;">◐</div>
                <h3 style="color: white;">Become a Gardener</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">Ready to get your hands dirty with the hard work of systems change? Join our growing network.</p>
                <a href="mailto:hello@act.place" class="btn" style="background: white; color: var(--act-sunrise);">Dig In</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: var(--act-empathy); color: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 3em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: white;">◯</div>
                <h3 style="color: white;">Water the Garden</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">Support regenerative innovation with resources, funding, or partnership opportunities.</p>
                <a href="mailto:hello@act.place" class="btn" style="background: white; color: var(--act-empathy);">Nourish Growth</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; padding: 40px; background: var(--act-cream); border-radius: 16px;">
            <p style="font-size: 1.3em; color: var(--act-soil); font-style: italic; margin: 0;">
                <span style="color: var(--act-seedling);">◆</span> "Every story is a seed. Every seed is a possibility. Every possibility is a future we cultivate together."
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

